{"id":"181a93c6-73b0-4cd5-969b-6ed06bc9bf86","name":"The All-Consuming Night: Tenebra Nyx","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(99, 7, 252);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">Their triumphs, their names, their dreams, all erased and devoured by the all-consuming night.</mark></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>The world has many legends.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>In those legends, there are mentions of all sorts of people.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Legendary Heroes.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Irredeemable Villains.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Brave Adventurers.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Cunning Schemers.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>All of these mentioned and more are usually the 'main characters' of these legends.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>They are presented as above and beyond the common folk or 'side characters' as one might call them.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Yet... certain things treat those 'main characters' like anyone else.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>The night is one of those things.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>In the face of the all-consuming night, all are the same and all will be devoured.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Be it through the one who embodies that night or through the inevitable force called time.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(99, 7, 252);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">Aspects of The Night:</mark></em></strong></span></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/image/ams28O79Cxh5j4uKHzkv6.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/image/T44dw0gX4I-Nfm_vDVLbh.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/image/JvjscDZekTsIyab6N_D35.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(99, 7, 252);\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/image/g5z64sEobjtSYWvaaIFrm.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">(Images Link: </mark></strong></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://imgur.com/a/me7jpqz\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(99, 7, 252);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">https://imgur.com/a/me7jpqz</mark></strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(99, 7, 252);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">)</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(99, 7, 252);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">Author's Note: This one was fun to make. Very ability focused.</mark></strong></span></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"NcTJxnZnFqvVl7F0wZzSv.webp","creator":"Dracob","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","🔮 Magical","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":5051,"messages":74653,"created_at":"2025-08-10T09:32:13.495997+00:00"}